  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to learn if using the ActiveStep™ treadmill reduces the number
      and severity of falls in older adults. This is a pilot study. The information collected will
      be used to support a grant application for a large multi-center trial in the future.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
